column5: Out with a bud, had tonnes of laughs and even caught a few walleyes, here's a nice one, we caught a few others and missed a bunch as well. Lots of perch caught but they all went back.
Forget the hockey talk for now, those are some really nice gold nuggets!
Nice fish Matt. I wont ever say anything about hockey...i dont understand it....lol.
Nice eyes. Sounds like a great time. Hope you watched your awesome sens  lol.  Those are some beast eyes though.
Good ones Matt!  And even though you didn't talk hockey and showed off some great fish, my bet is, the Laffs fans won't give ya any props brutha!!!
You lose the bet Drew.  I'm a huge Leafs fan, and, was the first one to give him props
yeah, yeah,  but just mention footie,.....
Good stuff Matt. Impressive walters ya got there.
